 Oh, understanding what a cell is, what an organism is, what substance is, and what mind is.

01:08:25.800 --> 01:08:47.800
 All of those, the biggest questions are still the most needing, clear understanding. Of what causes sickness and aging.

01:08:47.800 --> 01:08:56.800
 And so at the root of these questions are a deeper exploration of life that will move us into a different way of being, you think?

