 Yeah. If the present project of the ruling class goes ahead, basically everyone is a mechanical dead inside because they only have the role set for them by the outside system.

01:09:25.800 --> 01:09:52.800
 And if we all start living fully and realizing that the future is only ours to be lived and created, it should have nothing at all to do with the plans made in Davos or Washington or wherever.

